    <item>
      <title>法国努力阻止农民对巴黎的封锁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/france-scrambles-to-head-off-farmer-blockade-of-paris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府正在加紧阻止农民对巴黎的封锁，这些农民最近几天一直堵塞道路，以抗议更高的生产成本和严格的欧洲法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/france-scrambles-to-head-off-farmer-blockade-of-paris</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 10:54:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于自民党落后于新的极左集团，肖尔茨的联盟面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/scholz-s-coalition-under-pressure-as-fdp-lags-new-far-left-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨的执政联盟仍然面临压力，因为选民民意调查显示，共同执政的自由民主党落后于新的极左团体，并面临退出议会的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/scholz-s-coalition-under-pressure-as-fdp-lags-new-far-left-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 10:51:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
